{"tid":1253633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滅絕「克警」的奇謀，城大畢業生李卓軒控警務處長案（馮睎乾）","createTime":"2019-06-23T16:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T16:52:45.000Z","uid":263230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"447cd4b0373b11aef4f18c7e5423bb6f470493e5","tid":1253633,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190623/59745837?utm_campaign=hkad_social_AS.AppleDaily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3kjIEzesx8auGiaL8ZHMNhW4J2ODTYBM0wXnBAHZhhGKkmt26ZsVTucOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F59745837%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_AS.AppleDaily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3kjIEzesx8auGiaL8ZHMNhW4J2ODTYBM0wXnBAHZhhGKkmt26ZsVTucOg&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=7defd1de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F59745837%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_AS.AppleDaily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3kjIEzesx8auGiaL8ZHMNhW4J2ODTYBM0wXnBAHZhhGKkmt26ZsVTucOg&h=d5f5e3ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190623/59745837?utm_campaign=hkad_social_AS.AppleDaily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3kjIEzesx8auGiaL8ZHMNhW4J2ODTYBM0wXnBAHZhhGKkmt26ZsVTucOg</a><br />\n<br />\n律師友人L前晚傳來一則新聞，是城大畢業生李卓軒控警務處長案，他認為事有蹊蹺。李卓軒稱他在2014年佔旺期間，遭一名男警力抓陽具睾丸，使他痛楚徹骨，入稟向警方索償逾千萬元。案件原於十七日開審，但控辯雙方忽然同意和解，李卓軒需支付二三十萬元訟費。如此峰迴路轉，連法官李樹旭也感意外。李官明言，涉案錄影片段清晰顯示警方用了過度暴力，質疑控方何故撤控。控方律師僅表示李卓軒「無信心」。<br />\n<br />\n律師L為什麼覺得不尋常呢？一、李卓軒提出訴訟時還是大學生，資產應該不多，可能申請了法援，即使輸掉官司，訟費也不必擔心，何不繼續？二、由起訴到開審，經過幾年時間，雙方早已清楚錄影片段內容，連法官也講明片段「顯示警方用了過度暴力」，控方怎會開審前夕才突然「無信心」呢？<br />\n<br />\nL估計，這戲劇性變化或許跟六一二警方暴力事件有關&mdash;&mdash;若李勝訴，將會一石激起千層浪，引發史無前例的集體訴訟潮，嚴重打擊士氣。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控方願意忽然和解，到底是真的「無信心」，抑或有人眼見風頭火勢，寧願慷慨地私下賠償，而不想鬧上法庭呢？這是L最疑惑的一點。若他猜測屬實，大家可想像到檢控警察的阻力有多大了吧。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5b5fd60848abf1f542d1f21788af43aa09c7c599","tid":1253633,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea5fb2e1c5f96ea58c8c57047bd6b6e182a74d4d","tid":1253633,"uid":195650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:52:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}